Package: preprosim
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight Data Quality Simulation for Classification
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2016-05-15
Authors@R: person("Markus", "Vattulainen", email = "markus.vattulainen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package provides a function for quick sensitivity check of how adding of noise, missing
    values, outliers, low variance, irrelevant features, class swap (inconsistency), class imbalance
    and decrease in data volume affect classification accuracy for 'rpart' classification tree.
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    rpart,
    DMwR,
    reshape2,
    ggplot2,
    plyr,
    methods,
    stats,
    caret
Suggests:
    testthat,
    preprocomb,
    preproviz
URL: https://github.com/mvattulainen/preprosim
BugReports: https://github.com/mvattulainen/preprosim/issues
